cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques for part-of-speech (POS) tagging in Indonesian language. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which deals with NLP and related topics. The paper also explores various machine learning techniques, including neural networks, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) a likely category as well. Additionally, the use of neural networks suggests that cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) could also be a relevant category. The paper also mentions the evaluation of models, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
